    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338360/extras/de7bc57aafbe1303f24166b644a791bc.poster.avif?t=1698110215\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338360/extras/de7bc57aafbe1303f24166b644a791bc.webm?t=1698110215\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338360/extras/de7bc57aafbe1303f24166b644a791bc.mp4?t=1698110215\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>进入另一个世界的生活挣扎</strong></h2>欢迎来到一个受到《Forager》启发的世界，在这个世界里，由于一种诅咒，你每年只能醒来一次！醒来后，探索、掠夺、建造、扩张、通过与哥布林战斗来保卫你的领土，然后再进入沉睡，如此循环！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338360/extras/423c3fa7a46e467cfec9d99cf4b2dc7a.poster.avif?t=1698110215\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338360/extras/423c3fa7a46e467cfec9d99cf4b2dc7a.webm?t=1698110215\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338360/extras/423c3fa7a46e467cfec9d99cf4b2dc7a.mp4?t=1698110215\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>扩张与建造</strong></h2>建设你的城镇并确立其人口！建造瞭望塔、弓箭塔、兵营、安置村民，并在你沉睡一年的时候做好应对危险的准备！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338360/extras/e32a57c8670b6318da1df09d34fa8920.poster.avif?t=1698110215\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338360/extras/e32a57c8670b6318da1df09d34fa8920.webm?t=1698110215\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338360/extras/e32a57c8670b6318da1df09d34fa8920.mp4?t=1698110215\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>制作物品</strong></h2>利用收集到的资源制作各种工具和装备！这些物品将帮助你收集更多资源并实现成长！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338360/extras/096cdcbf21e730d674b403ebc0128512.poster.avif?t=1698110215\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338360/extras/096cdcbf21e730d674b403ebc0128512.webm?t=1698110215\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338360/extras/096cdcbf21e730d674b403ebc0128512.mp4?t=1698110215\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>交易</strong></h2>商人不时会经过这个地区。从这些商人那里购买不同的资源，或者出售你自己的资源！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338360/extras/1e6c1613ba39839268e64ad9e0807d9f.poster.avif?t=1698110215\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338360/extras/1e6c1613ba39839268e64ad9e0807d9f.webm?t=1698110215\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338360/extras/1e6c1613ba39839268e64ad9e0807d9f.mp4?t=1698110215\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>哥布林的威胁</strong></h2>这个世界充满了各种敌人，你可能会遇到哥布林等袭击性敌人！通过击败这些攻击性敌人来保卫领土！<br><br><i>&quot;每一次苏醒都是一次新的冒险，每一次重生都是变得更强大的机会！&quot;</i>",
